Title: Deploy DLP Policy (Financial Data)
Purpose: Deploy unified DLP policy to block external sharing of financial data

Prereq:
- Compliance admin / Exchange admin permissions
- Understand which endpoints your tenant supports (Graph Beta vs Compliance REST)

Steps:
1) Retrieve current DLP policy list
   GET https://graph.microsoft.com/beta/security/dlppolicies
2) Create new DLP policy
   POST https://graph.microsoft.com/beta/security/dlppolicies
   Body: templates/DLP-Protect-Financials.json
3) Assign policy to SharePoint/OneDrive/Exchange locations (add scope)
4) Test policy using sample documents (see tests/sample-documents)
5) Monitor incidents: GET https://graph.microsoft.com/beta/security/dlp/incidents

Verification:
- Policy appears in Compliance center
- Test documents produce an incident (check incidents endpoint)
